2026-05-05T03:57:46.7244443Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-05T03:57:46.7245136Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-05T03:57:46.7245802Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-05T03:57:46.7246462Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-05T03:57:46.7247126Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-05T03:57:46.7248036Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
